} 16. g4 Ne7 $11) 16. Nh4 $14 Qd7 (16... Bh7 $5 $14 {is worth looking at}) 17.
f4 $16 g5 (17... Nc6 $5 18. Bd5+ Be6 19. Bxc6 Qxc6 20. fxe5 Nc7 $16) 18. Nxf5
