Nxe7 29. Rf7 Ng6 (29... Ng8 {a fruitless try to alter the course of the game}
30. Be4 Nef6 31. Nxf6 Nxf6 32. Rxf6 d5 $18) 30. Rxa7 (30. Be4 $142 {secures
victory} Kg8 31. Bxg6 $18) 30... Ne5 31. Be4 (31. a4 {might be the shorter path
