is clearly inferior} dxc2 35. Re1 d4 $15) 34... Nxd3 35. Bf1 Nxb2 36. Bb5 $18)
32. Kg2 (32. Rb7 {keeps an even firmer grip} Kf8 33. Rxb6 Ke7 $18) 32... b5 (
